Photo: Xinhua Xi Jinping, general secretary of the Communist Party of China Central Committee, on Monday inspected Chaozhou, South China's Guangdong Province.

Photo: Xinhua Xi first visited the Guangji Bridge, Guangji Tower, and Paifang Street in Chaozhou to inspect the restoration and protection of cultural relics, the inheritance of intangible cultural heritage, and the development of cultural tourism resources. 

Photo: Xinhua

